00:14:54.408 --> 00:14:56.343 position:27% line:83% align:start
-So this is the
suspicious activity

00:14:56.377 --> 00:14:57.713 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yamaguchi tried
to warn you about,

00:14:57.746 --> 00:14:59.648 position:19% line:83% align:start
