00:15:24.039 --> 00:15:25.774 position:24% line:83% align:start
in for some bogus
medical checkups,

00:15:25.807 --> 00:15:27.743 position:21% line:83% align:start
and they planted the
interceptors in them.

00:15:27.776 --> 00:15:29.811 position:19% line:83% align:start
As far as I can tell,
every guy in the department

00:15:29.845 --> 00:15:32.048 position:21% line:83% align:start
