something behind this.

00:15:49.766 --> 00:15:51.399 position:30% line:89% align:start
-It's strange.

00:15:51.433 --> 00:15:52.668 position:16% line:83% align:start
There are detectives who
have been assigned to monitor

00:15:52.702 --> 00:15:56.005 position:7% line:83% align:start
Serano, and they've also been
implanted with interceptors.

00:15:56.038 --> 00:15:57.774 position:24% line:83% align:start
Neither Serano nor
the agents know

00:15:57.807 --> 00:16:00.076 position:19% line:83% align:start
these interceptors are
recording everything.

00:16:00.109 --> 00:16:02.979 position:13% line:83% align:start
-For friends, they're sure
not on very good terms.

00:16:03.012 --> 00:16:05.448 position:19% line:83% align:start
-We've got the pieces
of the puzzle now.

00:16:05.481 --> 00:16:07.817 position:19% line:83% align:start
So we need to move on
this as soon as possible.

00:16:07.850 --> 00:16:11.454 position:19% line:83% align:start
But we don't have the
goods to confront them yet.

00:16:11.487 --> 00:16:13.556 position:21% line:83% align:start
-In that case, let's
shake them up a little.

00:16:16.492 --> 00:16:19.562 position:24% line:89% align:start
