sensory surveillance technique.

00:16:27.603 --> 00:16:29.705 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Superintendent Daido
called a press conference?

00:16:29.739 --> 00:16:32.842 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Looks like we got a bigger
reaction than we imagined.

00:16:32.875 --> 00:16:35.645 position:7% line:83% align:start
-Daido was in charge the first
time Laughing Man struck,

00:16:35.678 --> 00:16:37.814 position:24% line:83% align:start
