initial investigations.

00:16:37.847 --> 00:16:40.050 position:5% line:83% align:start
It looks like there's something
his people want to keep

00:16:40.083 --> 00:16:43.120 position:7% line:83% align:start
in house, and they're going to
great lengths to cover it up.

00:16:43.153 --> 00:16:47.623 position:10% line:83% align:start
MAN: Thank you, gentlemen.
We're ready for your statement.

00:16:47.657 --> 00:16:50.761 position:5% line:83% align:start
-Last week, certain publications
alleged that interceptors were

00:16:50.794 --> 00:16:54.731 position:5% line:83% align:start
being used in violation of legal
standards, standards that were

00:16:54.765 --> 00:16:57.668 position:19% line:83% align:start
set out by the Sensory
Perception Surveillance Act.

00:16:57.701 --> 00:17:00.637 position:19% line:83% align:start
Therefore, an internal
investigation was ordered.

00:17:00.671 --> 00:17:03.140 position:19% line:83% align:start
Subsequently, Captain
Kunihiko Nibu,

00:17:03.173 --> 00:17:05.442 position:27% line:83% align:start
Chief of Special
Investigations Unit,

00:17:05.475 --> 00:17:08.579 position:13% line:83% align:start
admitted to participating
in these acts.

00:17:08.612 --> 00:17:10.848 position:19% line:83% align:start
After the Laughing Man
investigation hit a dead end,

00:17:10.881 --> 00:17:13.784 position:13% line:83% align:start
Captain Nibu attempted to
gather additional information

00:17:13.817 --> 00:17:16.119 position:13% line:83% align:start
by implanting interceptors
in his detectives

00:17:16.153 --> 00:17:18.989 position:5% line:89% align:start
against department regulations.

00:17:19.022 --> 00:17:22.025 position:21% line:83% align:start
Captain Nibu regrets
having taken these actions.

00:17:22.059 --> 00:17:25.062 position:10% line:83% align:start
He stated that he lost sound
judgment due to stress caused

00:17:25.096 --> 00:17:27.731 position:5% line:89% align:start
by severe setbacks in the case.

00:17:27.764 --> 00:17:30.101 position:7% line:83% align:start
Despite the captain's apology,
the fact of the matter

00:17:30.134 --> 00:17:33.770 position:5% line:83% align:start
is his actions deviated from his
professional responsibilities.

00:17:33.804 --> 00:17:36.074 position:27% line:83% align:start
Therefore, as of
today, Captain Nibu

00:17:36.107 --> 00:17:39.043 position:13% line:83% align:start
has been given an official
disciplinary dismissal.

00:17:39.077 --> 00:17:40.744 position:24% line:83% align:start
And we offer those
investigators who

00:17:40.777 --> 00:17:43.513 position:10% line:83% align:start
were assigned to this case,
as well as their families,

00:17:43.547 --> 00:17:47.517 position:21% line:83% align:start
our deepest and most
sincere apologies.

00:17:47.551 --> 00:17:48.786 position:24% line:83% align:start
PRESS MEMBER: What
about senior officials?

00:17:48.820 --> 00:17:50.121 position:16% line:89% align:start
