00:17:53.658 --> 00:17:55.459 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Wasn't there a
conflict of interest

00:17:55.492 --> 00:17:57.795 position:19% line:83% align:start
when Serano sold these
devices to the police?

00:17:57.829 --> 00:18:00.164 position:19% line:83% align:start
-I was told the agency
followed strict guidelines

00:18:00.198 --> 00:18:01.799 position:5% line:89% align:start
when it purchased these devices.

00:18:01.833 --> 00:18:03.835 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's my understanding
that they were selected

00:18:03.868 --> 00:18:07.105 position:5% line:83% align:start
through a formal bidding system
that is carefully regulated.

00:18:07.138 --> 00:18:08.873 position:24% line:83% align:start
PRESS MEMBER: What
kind of answer is that?

00:18:08.907 --> 00:18:12.710 position:7% line:83% align:start
Wasn't it the police who asked
for this new surveillance law?

00:18:12.744 --> 00:18:13.645 position:44% line:89% align:start
-Ha.

00:18:13.678 --> 00:18:15.580 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Uh, sir, is it true
that you're planning

00:18:15.613 --> 00:18:17.649 position:24% line:83% align:start
to retire soon and
relocate to Holland?

00:18:17.682 --> 00:18:19.617 position:30% line:83% align:start
And is it also
true that Serano's

00:18:19.651 --> 00:18:21.019 position:19% line:83% align:start
corporate headquarters
are in Holland?

00:18:21.052 --> 00:18:24.555 position:33% line:83% align:start
Is there any
connection there, sir?

00:18:24.589 --> 00:18:25.657 position:24% line:83% align:start
SERANO: Those are
personal questions

00:18:25.690 --> 00:18:27.458 position:33% line:83% align:start
