obligated to answer.

00:18:27.492 --> 00:18:28.893 position:24% line:83% align:start
PRESS MEMBER: What
does that mean?

00:18:28.927 --> 00:18:31.696 position:27% line:89% align:start
-Never changes.

00:18:31.729 --> 00:18:32.398 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's weird.

00:18:32.430 --> 00:18:34.465 position:5% line:89% align:start
Is the cameraman drunk or what?

00:18:34.499 --> 00:18:43.876 position:24% line:89% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: You

00:18:43.909 --> 00:18:46.477 position:41% line:83% align:start
a bit,
Superintendent-General Daido.

00:18:46.511 --> 00:18:49.547 position:16% line:83% align:start
Pleased to meet you, but
you already know who I am,

00:18:49.580 --> 00:18:50.983 position:35% line:89% align:start
don't you?

00:18:51.016 --> 00:18:53.819 position:24% line:89% align:start
[crowd muttering]

00:18:53.852 --> 00:18:55.254 position:33% line:89% align:start
-That's him.

00:18:55.287 --> 00:18:56.789 position:7% line:89% align:start
-What's wrong with this thing?

00:19:01.694 --> 00:19:02.995 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Hey, what's the
matter with Takakawa?

00:19:06.098 --> 00:19:09.501 position:19% line:83% align:start
-You know, Mr. Daido,
I tried to avoid this.

00:19:09.535 --> 00:19:13.038 position:10% line:83% align:start
I didn't want to be involved
