00:19:13.072 --> 00:19:15.107 position:24% line:83% align:start
I was honestly fed
up with you people

00:19:15.140 --> 00:19:18.110 position:27% line:83% align:start
and your rotting
rubbish heap of a world.

00:19:18.143 --> 00:19:20.646 position:16% line:83% align:start
So I haven't interfered
with the little farce you've

00:19:20.679 --> 00:19:23.283 position:24% line:83% align:start
been staging since
the incident occurred,

00:19:23.316 --> 00:19:26.785 position:7% line:89% align:start
even though I knew everything.

00:19:26.819 --> 00:19:30.123 position:7% line:83% align:start
You could say I was exhausted
from my fruitless exertions.

00:19:35.228 --> 00:19:36.930 position:16% line:89% align:start
-Hey, you watching this?

00:19:36.963 --> 00:19:39.065 position:19% line:83% align:start
That guy's cyberbrain
is being hacked.

00:19:39.099 --> 00:19:41.734 position:7% line:83% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: But I've changed
my mind, because, well, this

00:19:41.768 --> 00:19:44.204 position:24% line:83% align:start
show you've put on
today is pitiful.

00:19:44.237 --> 00:19:46.172 position:5% line:89% align:start
