00:19:53.947 --> 00:19:55.582 position:21% line:83% align:start
You and your comedy
troupe are going

00:19:55.615 --> 00:19:57.984 position:27% line:83% align:start
to reconvene in
three days, right?

00:19:58.018 --> 00:20:01.254 position:19% line:83% align:start
