truth this time, won't you?

00:20:01.287 --> 00:20:03.023 position:27% line:83% align:start
Because when the
curtain goes up,

00:20:03.056 --> 00:20:05.291 position:19% line:83% align:start
if you put on another
performance that rings as false

00:20:05.325 --> 00:20:11.931 position:7% line:83% align:start
as this one, I will be forced
to remove you from the stage.

00:20:11.965 --> 00:20:13.133 position:35% line:89% align:start
-Takakawa.

00:20:13.166 --> 00:20:13.933 position:24% line:89% align:start
Call an ambulance.

00:20:13.967 --> 00:20:16.169 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hurry!

00:20:16.203 --> 00:20:19.806 position:10% line:83% align:start
-And we are now returning to
