01:09:20.997 --> 01:09:22.999 position:19% line:83% align:start
They're going to think
that I've betrayed them.

01:09:23.033 --> 01:09:24.868 position:13% line:83% align:start
MAN: If I hadn't arranged
for this to happene,

01:09:24.901 --> 01:09:27.704 position:13% line:83% align:start
you never would have taken
the matter seriously.

01:09:27.737 --> 01:09:29.039 position:21% line:83% align:start
-You have to realize
that they're not

01:09:29.072 --> 01:09:31.275 position:21% line:83% align:start
as forgiving as you
seem to believe.

01:09:31.308 --> 01:09:33.743 position:13% line:83% align:start
-I feel bad about framing
you for the theft.

01:09:33.777 --> 01:09:36.613 position:13% line:83% align:start
I hope you can understand
why I had to resort to that.

01:09:36.646 --> 01:09:38.115 position:27% line:83% align:start
But I swore that
I wouldn't give up

01:09:38.149 --> 01:09:39.950 position:16% line:83% align:start
until I had exposed the
truth of what went on

01:09:39.984 --> 01:09:42.887 position:27% line:83% align:start
behind the micro
machine treatments.

01:09:42.920 --> 01:09:44.754 position:13% line:89% align:start
-How can you be so naive?

01:09:44.788 --> 01:09:46.323 position:33% line:83% align:start
Research in
cyberbrain technology

01:09:46.357 --> 01:09:48.625 position:19% line:83% align:start
was advancing in other
fields back then.

01:09:48.658 --> 01:09:50.294 position:24% line:83% align:start
If I had approved
the vaccine, people

01:09:50.327 --> 01:09:51.962 position:21% line:83% align:start
might have rejected
that technology

01:09:51.996 --> 01:09:53.898 position:10% line:89% align:start
and impeded its development.

01:09:53.931 --> 01:09:56.000 position:24% line:83% align:start
-What a convenient
excuse that is.

01:09:56.033 --> 01:09:57.735 position:30% line:83% align:start
Micro Machine
Industries, the company

01:09:57.768 --> 01:09:59.303 position:30% line:83% align:start
whose board of
directors you sat on,

01:09:59.336 --> 01:10:02.039 position:5% line:83% align:start
received approval only one month
after filing it paperwork--

01:10:02.073 --> 01:10:04.842 position:21% line:83% align:start
very quick and easy,
just like Serano.

01:10:04.875 --> 01:10:06.677 position:21% line:83% align:start
And thanks to that,
you people raked

01:10:06.710 --> 01:10:08.646 position:19% line:83% align:start
in profits of nearly a
trillion yen per year

01:10:08.679 --> 01:10:10.714 position:24% line:83% align:start
by selling protein
granules that have

01:10:10.748 --> 01:10:12.850 position:19% line:83% align:start
no effect no effect on
cyberbrain sclerosis.

01:10:12.883 --> 01:10:15.152 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's a blatant act
of fraud perpetrated

01:10:15.186 --> 01:10:17.021 position:21% line:83% align:start
under the direction
of the state.

01:10:17.054 --> 01:10:19.156 position:13% line:83% align:start
What excuses do you intend
to offer those patients who

01:10:19.190 --> 01:10:21.892 position:13% line:83% align:start
died not knowing this and
kept paying their treatment

01:10:21.926 --> 01:10:24.196 position:16% line:83% align:start
fees in the belief that
it actually worked?

01:10:24.229 --> 01:10:26.097 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Micro machines
nowadays are showing

01:10:26.131 --> 01:10:28.065 position:27% line:83% align:start
a certain degree
of effectiveness.

01:10:28.100 --> 01:10:31.702 position:5% line:83% align:start
If you look at the situation in
terms of sclerosis prevention,

01:10:31.735 --> 01:10:34.973 position:7% line:83% align:start
you can't say that nothing of
benefit came from our decision.

01:10:35.006 --> 01:10:36.308 position:35% line:89% align:start
-Benefit?

01:10:36.341 --> 01:10:37.976 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, then, if that's
the case, why aren't you

01:10:38.009 --> 01:10:39.377 position:19% line:83% align:start
treating yourself with
the micro machines?

01:10:51.323 --> 01:10:52.924 position:16% line:89% align:start
-Here, come take a look.

01:10:52.958 --> 01:10:56.194 position:41% line:89% align:start
-Huh?

01:10:56.228 --> 01:10:58.296 position:21% line:83% align:start
Isn't he an author?
-That's right.

01:10:58.330 --> 01:11:01.233 position:16% line:83% align:start
There are also artists,
former star athletes.

01:11:01.266 --> 01:11:03.935 position:24% line:83% align:start
And this man is a
professor at Miyahama

01:11:03.969 --> 01:11:06.037 position:10% line:83% align:start
University's medical school.
-Wait a minute.

01:11:06.071 --> 01:11:07.038 position:21% line:83% align:start
There are even names
of politicians.

01:11:07.072 --> 01:11:08.773 position:41% line:89% align:start
-Yes.

01:11:08.807 --> 01:11:10.242 position:19% line:83% align:start
And someone even more
critical to our cause

01:11:10.275 --> 01:11:14.146 position:19% line:89% align:start
is taking the vaccine.

01:11:14.179 --> 01:11:16.781 position:24% line:89% align:start
Can you spot him?

01:11:16.815 --> 01:11:18.850 position:27% line:83% align:start
TOGUSA: Hisashi
Imakurusu, chairman

01:11:18.884 --> 01:11:21.019 position:10% line:83% align:start
of the board of the Central
Drug Evaluation Council?

01:11:21.052 --> 01:11:25.056 position:5% line:83% align:start
Are you saying the chairman who
rejected the Murai vaccine is

01:11:25.090 --> 01:11:26.925 position:5% line:89% align:start
dependent on that same medicine?

01:11:26.958 --> 01:11:28.161 position:41% line:89% align:start
-Yes.

01:11:28.194 --> 01:11:31.397 position:5% line:83% align:start
