from Mr. Imakurusu himself.

01:11:31.430 --> 01:11:33.399 position:10% line:89% align:start
-What does all of this mean?

01:11:33.432 --> 01:11:36.269 position:5% line:83% align:start
-He's claiming that he's grown
exhausted from having to remain

01:11:36.302 --> 01:11:40.206 position:19% line:83% align:start
