01:11:41.941 --> 01:11:44.944 position:16% line:83% align:start
However, he deliberately
suppressed the Murai

01:11:44.977 --> 01:11:47.246 position:5% line:89% align:start
vaccine out of ulterior motives.

01:11:47.280 --> 01:11:49.815 position:24% line:83% align:start
Now, Imakurusu has
given his solemn word

01:11:49.849 --> 01:11:51.984 position:21% line:83% align:start
to stand up in court
in front of a judge

01:11:52.018 --> 01:11:54.120 position:16% line:83% align:start
and divulge this motive
that only he knows.

01:11:54.153 --> 01:11:56.322 position:24% line:83% align:start
-You mean the drug
evaluation chairman

01:11:56.355 --> 01:12:00.092 position:7% line:83% align:start
is gonna testify as to why he
wouldn't approve the vaccine?

01:12:00.126 --> 01:12:01.027 position:38% line:89% align:start
-Uh-huh.

01:12:01.060 --> 01:12:02.995 position:10% line:89% align:start
This time, victory is ours.

01:12:03.029 --> 01:12:03.497 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:12:03.530 --> 01:12:04.464 position:27% line:89% align:start
[loud rumbling]

01:12:38.165 --> 01:12:41.034 position:21% line:83% align:start
-The DEA's Narcotics
Suppression Squad.

01:12:41.068 --> 01:12:42.202 position:35% line:83% align:start
[coughing]
-Move it.

01:12:42.236 --> 01:12:42.735 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on.

01:12:42.768 --> 01:12:43.937 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hurry and kill them.

01:12:43.971 --> 01:12:46.240 position:7% line:83% align:start
We can take our time and look
for our target afterwards.

01:12:46.273 --> 01:12:48.475 position:13% line:89% align:start
But first, kill them all!

01:12:48.508 --> 01:12:51.411 position:7% line:83% align:start
-They're from the Ministry of
Health, Labor, and Welfare.

01:12:51.445 --> 01:12:53.880 position:13% line:89% align:start
-Then they want the file?

01:12:53.914 --> 01:12:54.982 position:5% line:89% align:start
-You've got to get out of here.

01:12:55.015 --> 01:12:56.149 position:27% line:83% align:start
These people are
trained assassins.

01:12:56.183 --> 01:12:57.985 position:21% line:89% align:start
They will kill you.

01:12:58.018 --> 01:12:59.520 position:24% line:89% align:start
-Just who are you?

01:12:59.554 --> 01:13:00.921 position:13% line:89% align:start
-I'm with Public Security.

01:13:06.026 --> 01:13:07.894 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Oops, some of our
boys got taken down.

01:13:20.541 --> 01:13:23.544 position:21% line:83% align:start
We need to take some
losses on our side, too.

01:13:23.578 --> 01:13:26.847 position:7% line:83% align:start
That's just how reality works.
Right?

01:13:49.037 --> 01:13:50.938 position:13% line:89% align:start
Now, go search the corpse.

01:13:50.972 --> 01:13:58.246 position:33% line:89% align:start
[chuckling]

01:13:58.279 --> 01:13:59.247 position:35% line:89% align:start
-A cyborg?

01:14:16.231 --> 01:14:19.368 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Ah, now things are
getting interesting.

01:14:19.401 --> 01:14:20.602 position:27% line:89% align:start
Got a survivor.

01:14:20.636 --> 01:14:21.969 position:30% line:89% align:start
Get over here.

01:14:26.941 --> 01:14:28.143 position:30% line:89% align:start
Tell you what.

01:14:28.177 --> 01:14:30.212 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll give you a running
start before I shoot.

01:14:34.249 --> 01:14:35.084 position:35% line:89% align:start
Ah, damn.

01:14:35.117 --> 01:14:37.653 position:27% line:83% align:start
That was our own
truck I just shot up.

01:14:37.686 --> 01:14:41.590 position:27% line:83% align:start
Go on, get down
there and kill him.

01:14:41.623 --> 01:14:43.225 position:41% line:89% align:start
-Shit.

01:14:43.258 --> 01:14:45.160 position:21% line:83% align:start
Maybe I should have
gone full cyborg, too.

01:14:53.636 --> 01:14:55.371 position:30% line:83% align:start
TOGUSA: Major.
Chief.

01:14:55.404 --> 01:14:57.005 position:27% line:89% align:start
I've been shot.

01:15:05.582 --> 01:15:08.451 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Bureau Chief, we've
completed the op.

01:15:08.485 --> 01:15:10.453 position:16% line:89% align:start
But the item is a copy.

01:15:10.487 --> 01:15:12.622 position:24% line:89% align:start
-What did you say?

01:15:12.655 --> 01:15:14.957 position:10% line:89% align:start
-We know where it came from.

