01:26:43.124 --> 01:26:44.892 position:30% line:89% align:start
Can't breathe.

01:26:44.926 --> 01:26:46.060 position:38% line:89% align:start
Please.

01:26:46.094 --> 01:26:47.361 position:30% line:89% align:start
Pop the hatch.

01:26:53.101 --> 01:26:55.370 position:24% line:83% align:start
-A little closer.
Good.

01:27:09.050 --> 01:27:10.285 position:13% line:89% align:start
Get this guy aboard, ASAP.

01:27:13.921 --> 01:27:15.690 position:30% line:89% align:start
What a moron.

01:27:15.723 --> 01:27:17.159 position:35% line:89% align:start
Wait here.

01:27:17.192 --> 01:27:18.427 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hey, hold it right there.

01:27:18.460 --> 01:27:22.030 position:33% line:83% align:start
Both of you.
Good.

01:27:22.064 --> 01:27:22.998 position:24% line:89% align:start
Don't even blink.

01:27:23.031 --> 01:27:23.899 position:35% line:89% align:start
Imakurusu.

01:27:38.947 --> 01:27:40.682 position:13% line:83% align:start
BATOU: Our guy's been hit.
Requesting ambulance.

01:27:46.088 --> 01:27:50.325 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Laughing Man, is that
what you really look like?

01:27:50.359 --> 01:27:53.262 position:30% line:89% align:start
-What's that?

01:27:53.295 --> 01:27:54.930 position:24% line:89% align:start
The Laughing Man?

01:27:54.963 --> 01:27:55.931 position:24% line:89% align:start
What does he mean?

01:27:55.964 --> 01:28:01.837 position:41% line:89% align:start
Wait.

01:28:01.870 --> 01:28:08.844 position:30% line:83% align:start
This file is--
optical camouflage?

01:28:08.877 --> 01:28:11.080 position:24% line:89% align:start
No, that's not it.

01:28:11.114 --> 01:28:12.215 position:33% line:89% align:start
You bastard.

01:28:12.248 --> 01:28:13.416 position:10% line:89% align:start
I know why I can't see you.

01:28:13.449 --> 01:28:14.816 position:21% line:89% align:start
You hacked my eyes.

01:28:22.791 --> 01:28:23.960 position:30% line:89% align:start
Where are you?

01:28:23.993 --> 01:28:24.994 position:24% line:89% align:start
Are you close by?

01:28:28.231 --> 01:28:29.999 position:16% line:89% align:start
Where the hell are you?

01:28:50.253 --> 01:28:51.488 position:30% line:89% align:start
-They're here.

01:28:51.522 --> 01:28:53.756 position:24% line:83% align:start
Aramaki won't get
any further than me.

01:28:53.790 --> 01:28:54.458 position:30% line:89% align:start
Tell him that.

01:28:54.491 --> 01:28:55.892 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Yes, sir.
I understand.

01:29:05.236 --> 01:29:07.438 position:35% line:89% align:start
[knocking]

01:29:07.471 --> 01:29:09.406 position:27% line:89% align:start
CHIEF: Come in.

01:29:09.440 --> 01:29:11.175 position:33% line:89% align:start
-Pardon us.

01:29:11.208 --> 01:29:14.378 position:10% line:83% align:start
Bureau Chief Niimi, I have a
warrant here for your arrest.

01:29:14.411 --> 01:29:16.981 position:16% line:83% align:start
You're being charged in
the murder conspiracy tied

01:29:17.014 --> 01:29:19.283 position:21% line:83% align:start
to the investigation
for Sunflower Society,

01:29:19.316 --> 01:29:21.418 position:21% line:83% align:start
as well as the death
of Mr. Imakurusu.

01:29:21.452 --> 01:29:25.022 position:21% line:83% align:start
If you would please
come with us.

01:29:25.055 --> 01:29:27.324 position:19% line:83% align:start
-I heard what happened
with the narc squad.

01:29:27.358 --> 01:29:30.194 position:7% line:83% align:start
But it's absurd to think that
I had anything to do whatsoever

01:29:30.227 --> 01:29:32.129 position:21% line:83% align:start
with the ordering of
Imakurusu's death.

01:29:32.162 --> 01:29:36.133 position:10% line:83% align:start
The head of the narc squad,
a man named Gayle Yasuoka,

01:29:36.166 --> 01:29:39.003 position:16% line:83% align:start
is much more willing to
talk than we expected.

01:29:39.036 --> 01:29:41.939 position:16% line:83% align:start
You see, he recorded his
conversations with you.

01:29:41.972 --> 01:29:44.441 position:5% line:89% align:start
And he is being most cooperate.

01:29:44.476 --> 01:29:46.143 position:24% line:83% align:start
We know about the
Laughing Man incident

01:29:46.176 --> 01:29:49.346 position:16% line:83% align:start
and how it motivated you
to have Imakurusu killed.

01:29:49.381 --> 01:29:52.216 position:10% line:83% align:start
So as you can see, you and I
have a great deal to discuss.

01:29:52.249 --> 01:29:55.886 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Fine.
Let's get this over with.

01:29:55.919 --> 01:29:56.421 position:27% line:89% align:start
-Take him away.

01:30:09.033 --> 01:30:12.537 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Batou, I want you to
investigate the narc squad

01:30:12.570 --> 01:30:15.006 position:10% line:83% align:start
and find out why they would
go to such extreme measures

01:30:15.040 --> 01:30:16.941 position:27% line:83% align:start
to retrieve the
vaccine recipient list.

01:30:16.975 --> 01:30:19.044 position:19% line:89% align:start
Find the real reason.

01:30:19.077 --> 01:30:21.546 position:21% line:83% align:start
Another thing-- the
surviving members

01:30:21.579 --> 01:30:23.882 position:27% line:83% align:start
may be lying low
somewhere out there.

01:30:23.915 --> 01:30:25.283 position:35% line:89% align:start
Watch out.

01:30:25.317 --> 01:30:27.419 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'll head back when
we're done with Niimi.

01:30:27.452 --> 01:30:30.355 position:30% line:89% align:start
Over and out.

01:30:30.388 --> 01:30:32.590 position:27% line:83% align:start
-The chief, huh?
-Yeah.

01:30:32.624 --> 01:30:35.594 position:16% line:83% align:start
The chief just arrested
some bureaucrat named Niimi.

01:30:35.628 --> 01:30:38.530 position:13% line:83% align:start
Looks like he was the man
behind the narc squad.

01:30:38.564 --> 01:30:40.265 position:35% line:89% align:start
-That so?

01:30:40.298 --> 01:30:43.001 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, at least my getting
perforated was worth something.

01:30:43.034 --> 01:30:45.538 position:24% line:83% align:start
But what was that
powered exoskeleton?

01:30:45.571 --> 01:30:47.640 position:24% line:83% align:start
-A little toy the
narc squad was somehow

01:30:47.673 --> 01:30:50.175 position:10% line:89% align:start
able to get their hands on.

01:30:50.208 --> 01:30:51.610 position:19% line:89% align:start
The major took it on.

01:30:51.644 --> 01:30:53.512 position:19% line:83% align:start
She overheated in the
fight, and now she's

01:30:53.546 --> 01:30:55.381 position:5% line:89% align:start
swapping her body for a new one.

01:30:55.414 --> 01:30:57.483 position:24% line:83% align:start
TOGUSA: Is she OK?
BATOU: Well, yeah.

01:30:57.516 --> 01:31:02.355 position:5% line:83% align:start
But, uh-- what you said before
about your eyes getting hacked?

01:31:02.388 --> 01:31:06.024 position:13% line:89% align:start
Same thing happened to me.

01:31:06.057 --> 01:31:06.726 position:30% line:89% align:start
See you later.

01:31:06.759 --> 01:31:09.161 position:7% line:89% align:start
I've got a ton of stuff to do.

01:31:09.195 --> 01:31:10.329 position:19% line:83% align:start
Here, I'll leave this
with you for now.

01:31:16.268 --> 01:31:17.570 position:27% line:89% align:start
-This is-- wait.

01:31:17.603 --> 01:31:18.471 position:10% line:89% align:start
You mean the Laughing Man--

01:31:41.026 --> 01:31:43.396 position:27% line:83% align:start
-I apologize for
keeping you waiting.

01:31:43.429 --> 01:31:45.264 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'll be in charge.

01:31:45.297 --> 01:31:48.100 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm Sano.

01:31:48.134 --> 01:31:50.604 position:27% line:83% align:start
This isn't your
first time, right?

01:31:50.637 --> 01:31:51.571 position:13% line:89% align:start
There's no need to worry.

01:31:51.605 --> 01:31:53.205 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'll be gentle.

01:32:00.012 --> 01:32:01.080 position:27% line:89% align:start
All right, then.

01:32:01.113 --> 01:32:03.316 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm just gonna take a
little look under the hood,

01:32:03.350 --> 01:32:04.351 position:24% line:89% align:start
if you don't mind.

01:32:07.287 --> 01:32:08.221 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, my.

01:32:08.255 --> 01:32:11.358 position:19% line:89% align:start
You have a fine body.

01:32:11.391 --> 01:32:12.559 position:33% line:89% align:start
[chuckling]

01:32:29.576 --> 01:32:31.211 position:27% line:89% align:start
How you feeling?

01:32:31.244 --> 01:32:33.146 position:19% line:89% align:start
Does your brain hurt?

01:32:33.180 --> 01:32:35.048 position:21% line:83% align:start
-That supposed to be
some kind of joke?

01:32:35.081 --> 01:32:36.684 position:16% line:83% align:start
The brain's not capable
of sensing pain.

01:32:36.717 --> 01:32:38.418 position:21% line:89% align:start
-Don't be like that.

01:32:38.452 --> 01:32:41.021 position:13% line:83% align:start
There's no reason we can't
take our time and enjoy this.

01:32:41.054 --> 01:32:43.023 position:21% line:83% align:start
Or could it be that
you don't like me?

01:32:43.056 --> 01:32:45.225 position:27% line:83% align:start
-No offense, but
that's it exactly.

01:32:45.258 --> 01:32:48.028 position:10% line:83% align:start
Now that we're both clear on
that, can we get on with this?

01:32:48.061 --> 01:32:50.297 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm in a bit of a rush.

01:32:50.331 --> 01:32:52.300 position:7% line:89% align:start
-My, someone's in a bad mood.

01:32:55.202 --> 01:32:58.071 position:21% line:83% align:start
I've decided to lock
down your speech center.

01:32:58.104 --> 01:33:00.608 position:19% line:83% align:start
Of course, it's not as
if someone would come

01:33:00.641 --> 01:33:04.245 position:13% line:83% align:start
to your rescue anyway, no
matter how loud you shouted.

01:33:12.253 --> 01:33:16.224 position:19% line:83% align:start
Ms. Kusanagi, how's my
little patient feeling now?

01:33:16.257 --> 01:33:17.091 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, my.

01:33:17.124 --> 01:33:19.260 position:24% line:83% align:start
What a rebellious
look in your eyes.

01:33:19.293 --> 01:33:21.629 position:19% line:89% align:start
That simply won't do.

01:33:21.662 --> 01:33:24.733 position:21% line:83% align:start
What do you think of
the world without red?

01:33:24.766 --> 01:33:27.736 position:13% line:89% align:start
Kind of pretty, isn't it?

01:33:27.769 --> 01:33:29.237 position:5% line:89% align:start
Don't get the wrong impression.

01:33:29.270 --> 01:33:32.473 position:21% line:83% align:start
I don't enjoy doing
barbaric things like this.

01:33:32.507 --> 01:33:35.376 position:5% line:89% align:start
But you left me with no choice.

01:33:35.409 --> 01:33:37.646 position:13% line:83% align:start
You and your friends went
a little too far this time.

01:33:42.784 --> 01:33:44.252 position:13% line:89% align:start
KUSANAGI: What's going on?

01:33:44.285 --> 01:33:46.588 position:21% line:83% align:start
Is this some kind of
joke at my expense?

01:33:46.622 --> 01:33:48.590 position:5% line:83% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: You're giving off
some unpleasant brain waves.

01:33:48.624 --> 01:33:50.425 position:21% line:83% align:start
Why not use my eyes
for the time being?

01:33:53.328 --> 01:33:56.198 position:41% line:89% align:start
-Huh?

01:33:56.231 --> 01:33:58.800 position:21% line:83% align:start
KUSANAGI: You're the
Laughing Man, aren't you?

01:33:58.834 --> 01:34:00.702 position:13% line:83% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: This is the
third time we've met, you know.

01:34:00.736 --> 01:34:01.670 position:21% line:89% align:start
And let me clarify.

01:34:01.703 --> 01:34:04.473 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm not the one who
came up with that name.

01:34:04.506 --> 01:34:06.141 position:7% line:83% align:start
KUSANAGI: It was very arrogant
of you to sneak in here,

01:34:06.174 --> 01:34:07.776 position:13% line:89% align:start
not to mention dangerous.

01:34:07.809 --> 01:34:09.177 position:10% line:89% align:start
What did you come here for?

01:34:09.211 --> 01:34:11.446 position:27% line:83% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: To
get you to help me.

01:34:11.480 --> 01:34:14.683 position:7% line:83% align:start
KUSANAGI: From where I stand,
you've got that backwards.

01:34:14.716 --> 01:34:15.551 position:13% line:89% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: True enough.

01:34:15.584 --> 01:34:17.319 position:24% line:83% align:start
You're not an easy
person to talk to.

01:34:17.352 --> 01:34:19.488 position:21% line:83% align:start
You see, my back is
against the wall,

01:34:19.521 --> 01:34:20.857 position:13% line:83% align:start
and you're the only option
I could come up with.

01:34:20.890 --> 01:34:23.125 position:27% line:83% align:start
I figure if that
son of a bitch God

01:34:23.158 --> 01:34:25.127 position:24% line:83% align:start
hasn't completely
turned his back on me,

01:34:25.160 --> 01:34:26.729 position:24% line:83% align:start
you might actually
lend me a hand.

01:34:26.763 --> 01:34:29.197 position:13% line:83% align:start
KUSANAGI: Blasphemous, and
yet polite at the same time.

01:34:29.231 --> 01:34:32.301 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're awfully full of
yourself, aren't you?

01:34:32.334 --> 01:34:33.502 position:24% line:83% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: I do
what I have to do.

01:34:33.535 --> 01:34:36.305 position:5% line:83% align:start
Failure is out of the question,
because if I don't succeed

01:34:36.338 --> 01:34:39.676 position:7% line:83% align:start
this time, all the phonies in
the world will be legitimized.

01:34:39.709 --> 01:34:41.644 position:7% line:83% align:start
KUSANAGI: Sounds to me as if
you've hoisted all the problems

01:34:41.678 --> 01:34:43.780 position:24% line:83% align:start
of the world onto
your shoulders.

01:34:43.813 --> 01:34:45.882 position:24% line:83% align:start
So what could the
hero of the net

01:34:45.915 --> 01:34:48.618 position:5% line:89% align:start
possibly want me to do for him?

01:34:48.651 --> 01:34:50.553 position:16% line:83% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: You could
start by listening to me.

01:34:50.587 --> 01:34:52.187 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm going to tell
you the whole story

01:34:52.220 --> 01:34:53.790 position:21% line:83% align:start
behind the Laughing
Man incident.

01:34:53.823 --> 01:34:55.858 position:10% line:83% align:start
After that, I'd like you to
stand back and do nothing

01:34:55.892 --> 01:34:58.328 position:5% line:89% align:start
while I face my final challenge.

01:34:58.361 --> 01:35:01.264 position:19% line:83% align:start
And if by some chance
I should fail and die,

01:35:01.297 --> 01:35:03.833 position:21% line:83% align:start
all I ask of you is
this-- that your people

01:35:03.866 --> 01:35:06.169 position:7% line:89% align:start
bring this incident to light.

01:35:06.202 --> 01:35:07.470 position:16% line:89% align:start
KUSANAGI: Unbelievable.

01:35:07.503 --> 01:35:09.238 position:27% line:89% align:start
All right, fine.

01:35:09.272 --> 01:35:11.274 position:13% line:83% align:start
As your captive audience,
I've listened to your words.

01:35:11.307 --> 01:35:12.875 position:13% line:89% align:start
Now, I have a few for you.

01:35:12.910 --> 01:35:15.812 position:10% line:83% align:start
The mark of an immature man
is that he wants to die nobly

01:35:15.846 --> 01:35:18.414 position:19% line:83% align:start
for a cause, while the
mark of a mature one

01:35:18.448 --> 01:35:20.216 position:21% line:83% align:start
is that he wants to
live humbly for one.

01:35:20.249 --> 01:35:21.852 position:19% line:89% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: Ah, yes.

01:35:21.885 --> 01:35:24.688 position:7% line:83% align:start
Written by the psychoanalyst,
Wilhelm Stekel.

01:35:24.722 --> 01:35:27.725 position:7% line:83% align:start
KUSANAGI: I sensed this about
you as soon as I met you.

01:35:27.758 --> 01:35:31.427 position:7% line:83% align:start
It's a quality that I dislike
intensely, Mr. Know It All.

01:35:31.461 --> 01:35:33.296 position:10% line:83% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: Seems like you
fall into the same category.

01:35:33.329 --> 01:35:37.635 position:7% line:83% align:start
But all you have to do is ask
for help, and I'd give it.

01:35:37.668 --> 01:35:40.303 position:16% line:83% align:start
KUSANAGI: Must be hatred
of one's own kind.

01:35:40.336 --> 01:35:40.938 position:41% line:89% align:start
Fine.

01:35:40.971 --> 01:35:42.539 position:13% line:89% align:start
Go do what you have to do.

01:35:42.573 --> 01:35:44.307 position:10% line:83% align:start
I don't know if I'll be able
to keep my word, though.

01:35:44.340 --> 01:35:46.577 position:24% line:83% align:start
LAUGHING MAN: If I
know you, you will.

01:35:55.486 --> 01:35:57.788 position:16% line:89% align:start
I leave you my memories.

01:35:57.821 --> 01:35:59.456 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm counting on you.

01:36:11.568 --> 01:36:13.270 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's up to you now.

01:36:22.346 --> 01:36:24.381 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Well, then, as much
as I'll miss you,

01:36:24.415 --> 01:36:27.886 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna let you
die peacefully now.

01:36:27.919 --> 01:36:28.787 position:33% line:89% align:start
The needles.

01:36:47.539 --> 01:36:48.606 position:30% line:89% align:start
-What's that?

01:36:48.640 --> 01:36:51.609 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Don't worry, it's nothing.
BATOU: Chief's calling.

01:36:51.643 --> 01:36:52.977 position:30% line:89% align:start
You done yet?

01:36:53.011 --> 01:36:53.845 position:21% line:89% align:start
KUSANAGI: I am now.

01:36:53.878 --> 01:37:03.321 position:44% line:89% align:start
-Hm.

01:37:24.309 --> 01:37:26.645 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Ishikawa, have any luck
drawing new testimonies out

01:37:26.679 --> 01:37:28.848 position:27% line:83% align:start
of the remaining
narc squad members?

01:37:28.881 --> 01:37:31.617 position:5% line:83% align:start
ISHIKAWA: We weren't able to get
much useful intel out of them.

01:37:31.650 --> 01:37:33.686 position:13% line:83% align:start
And there's the fact that
their boss, Director Niimi,

01:37:33.719 --> 01:37:35.788 position:30% line:83% align:start
just committed
cyberbrain suicide.

01:37:35.821 --> 01:37:38.057 position:21% line:83% align:start
So that lead turned
into a dead end.

01:37:38.090 --> 01:37:42.661 position:10% line:83% align:start
-And we haven't been able to
find the Laughing Man, either.

01:37:42.695 --> 01:37:44.463 position:30% line:89% align:start
-That's true.

01:37:44.497 --> 01:37:46.031 position:24% line:83% align:start
Now, we have a new
set of instructions.

01:37:46.065 --> 01:37:48.701 position:10% line:89% align:start
We're going after this guy.

01:37:48.734 --> 01:37:50.703 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Hey, that's--
-Right.

01:37:50.736 --> 01:37:53.072 position:10% line:83% align:start
Assemblyman Kaoru Yakushima,
standing secretary

01:37:53.105 --> 01:37:55.474 position:5% line:89% align:start
general of the ruling coalition.

01:37:55.508 --> 01:37:56.542 position:13% line:89% align:start
ISHIKAWA: Yakushima, huh?

01:37:56.575 --> 01:37:59.311 position:13% line:83% align:start
He's the most powerful man
in his party right now.

01:37:59.345 --> 01:38:00.813 position:21% line:83% align:start
And he was Minister
of Health at the time

01:38:00.846 --> 01:38:02.548 position:7% line:89% align:start
of the Laughing Man incident.

01:38:02.581 --> 01:38:05.718 position:5% line:83% align:start
BORMA: He's a die hard MHLW man
who built his current position

01:38:05.751 --> 01:38:07.887 position:13% line:83% align:start
by switching jurisdiction
of cyberbrain technology

01:38:07.921 --> 01:38:10.322 position:27% line:83% align:start
from METI to the
Ministry of Health.

01:38:10.356 --> 01:38:11.657 position:24% line:83% align:start
KUSANAGI: And it's
